<p>Thinks W. P. Garrison’s book [extracts from <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi> for juvenile readers] would serve as an advertisement for the <hi rend="italic">Journal</hi>.</p>  
<p>Disappointed at sale of <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>.</p> 
